text: Neuenhaus is a Samtgemeinde ("collective municipality") in Bentheim, in Lower Saxony, Germany. Its seat is in the municipality Neuenhaus. The Samtgemeinde Neuenhaus has the following municipalities: # Esche # Georgsdorf # Lage # Neuenhaus # Osterwald Category:Samtgemeinden in Lower Saxony
